message.content: It is not possible to provide a definitive summary of what most men in Canada think of abortion, as opinions on this issue can vary significantly among individuals. However, Canada generally has more liberal views on abortion compared to some other countries. Abortion is legal and accessible in the country, and a majority of Canadians support a woman's right to choose. Many men in Canada may support a woman's reproductive autonomy and believe that decisions regarding abortion should be made by the individual involved. However, it is important to note that opinions on abortion can differ among men in Canada based on various factors such as personal beliefs, religious background, and individual experiences.
